      • winDetector

        public Player winDetector(int row,
                          int column,
                          boolean updateGUI)
        Checks if a player has won the game and draws a special line in the GUI where the player won if desired
        Parameters:
        row - Row in which the last gem was set
        column - Column in which the last gem was set
        updateGUI - If true, a line will be drawn in the GUI at the spot where the player has won
        Returns:
        Player.Player1 if Player 1 has won, Player.Player2 if Player 2 has won, Player.PlayerTie if the game is a tie, null if the game is not finished yet
